{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_trtllm_disaggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries for TRT-LLM in disaggregated mode.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode TRT-LLM workers\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "509e6fb7-a162-4319-a9b9-5908c4d6d64e-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "80dbbe8d-14af-43a5-8066-4716872a299b-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "21379539-3672-49ea-87dc-f00945f15938-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'trtllm'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775684117068, "stop": 1775684263272, "uuid": "bd1a5f31-f86f-4feb-9448-f79baf91f734", "historyId": "322a5543bf79ff39110ed403ea9bc67f", "testCaseId": "115e9f32bd060fb7d9c10bca2ea295d9", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_trtllm#test_etcd_ha_failover_trtllm_disaggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "trtllm"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_1"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "trtllm"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha"}, {"name": "suite", "value": "test_trtllm"}, {"name": "host", "value": "prod-test